premise_source_doc_sentence: Nerruku Ner  (  Face to Face  )  is a 1997 Tamil dramatic thriller film written and directed by Vasanth and produced by Mani Ratnam .
The film features Vijay , Surya , Kausalya and Simran in lead roles .
Raghuvaran , Shanthi Krishna , Karan , Vivek , Manivannan and Prakash Raj form the ensemble cast , while Deva and K. V. Anand handled the film 's soundtrack and cinematography respectively .
It was dubbed into telugu as Mukha Mukhi .
